22
00:01:15,460 --> 00:01:19,956
A crisis of desire,
as in owning the wanting --

23
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:22,966
desire as an expression
of our individuality,

24
00:01:22,990 --> 00:01:26,955
of our free choice,
of our preferences, of our identity --

25
00:01:26,979 --> 00:01:30,281
desire that has become a central concept

26
00:01:30,305 --> 00:01:33,505
as part of modern love
and individualistic societies.

27
00:01:33,529 --> 00:01:36,746
You know, this is the first time
