34
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:07,340
So what sustains desire,
and why is it so difficult?

35
00:02:08,075 --> 00:02:12,883
And at the heart of sustaining
desire in a committed relationship,

36
00:02:12,907 --> 00:02:18,490
