47
00:02:51,093 --> 00:02:52,693
For journey, for travel.

48
00:02:53,068 --> 00:02:56,593
So reconciling our need for security
and our need for adventure

49
00:02:56,617 --> 00:02:58,167
into one relationship,

50
00:02:58,191 --> 00:03:01,050
